data.title: Gigabyte Z97 Series Motherboards Interview
data.description: Leon from Gigatyte was waiting to provide an overview of their newest 9-series motherboards. These Gaming, Performance, OC, and Black Edition motherboards feature the Z97 chipset as well as socket 1150 compatibility for Intel's 4th Generation Core CPUs, including "Haswell Refresh" and "Devil's Canyon" variants.

data.title: ASUS Z97 5 way Optimization Demo Interview
data.description: The new ASUS Z97 Mainstream series of motherboards feature 5-way optimization -- but what does that even mean? It means you can automatically overclock your CPU, optimize your power delivery and power saving features, tune all of your system fans, and set up application-specific profiles that will engage OC settings when you launch specific programs. J.J. is here to demonstrate and explain!

data.title: ASUS Z97 Deluxe Motherboard Interview
data.description: Paul and J.J. discuss the newest high-end offering from the ASUS Z97 Mainstream series: the Z97 Deluxe. If you're looking for the most feature-packed and future-proof motherboard outside of ASUS RoG, this is the board to buy.

data.title: ASUS Z97 Pro Motherboard Interview with J.J.
data.description: We know our viewers can't get enough of the extensive knowledge that J.J. from ASUS brings to the table, so we decided to bring him out to the studio for a look at their newest Z97 motherboards. Here's the ASUS Z97 Pro, featuring an updated color scheme and compatibility with Intel's 4th Generation Core CPUs, including the "Haswell Refresh" and "Devil's Canyon" models.
